            Lower cost for customer-acquisition - An existing, large customer base makes it easier to start new businesses.
          </div>
          <div class="right-up decorate">
            Non-tampered data - Borrowing contracts are encrypted and then stored on distributed ledgers on the blockchain.
          </div>
          <div class="left-middle decorate">
            Simplified process - With basic information and credit report verified, users don’t have to repeatedly fill out forms.
          </div>
          <div class="right-middle decorate">
            Lower risks - Order information accumulated on the blockchain, which provides reliable evidence for risk control agencies.
          </div>
          <div class="left-bottom decorate">
            Higher efficiency - With multiple credit agencies to choose from, risks become lower and lending becomes more efficient.
          </div>
          <div class="right-bottom decorate">
            Decentralized, transparent, and low-cost.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="title">
        Why join us
